{
  "stem": "9943.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And, and as I mentioned, my mother moved to Luck, where her parents lived.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] She was 15 years younger than myself, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Franka.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And she came one day to, to visit, visit me in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "A friend of, of, of ours, Mark Mark Rubenstein, was-- brought her.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] Again, it's a mixed situation, because my sister, Mina, was working for my-- the cousin-- one of the cousins there, with a daughter Franka's age.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Well, that would mean to introduce you to that, that aunt of mine, which I already talked about in Warsaw, who had three daughters and four sons.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] But I'll, I'll leave this for the time being because we'll have time to talk about it at some other opportunity.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I used to come to, to Luck for the provocation.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I met medical-- all kinds of students who, who came also at vacation time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[SIGHS] And when I-- it was after the second year of medicine, I went-- in summertime, I went to the local Jewish hospital in Luck, where the director was my future father-in-law, Dr.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Pemow, Friedman Pemow, that you heard about.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And his son was only a student at that time in, in near Danzig in Germany.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He studied to be an engineer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It was the only son they had, Zenobi, or, for short, [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Zonya ?].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And there was a, a, a flood.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And he came to take pictures of that flood in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "This is how we met.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we used to go, all of us, used to go to the beach.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "There is a Styr-- a river, Styr, in Luck.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
